## Source Datasets

The generated datasets are derived from the following publicly available chest X-ray repositories:
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/tawsifurrahman/covid19-radiography-database
This dataset is released under Kaggleâ€™s open data terms for research and educational use and contains fully anonymized chest X-ray images. The dataset does not include personally identifiable information, and no additional permissions are required for its use in academic publications.
The Montgomery County Tuberculosis Chest X-ray Dataset is provided by the U.S. National Library of Medicine (NLM), National Institutes of Health (NIH), and is publicly accessible at:
https://data.lhncbc.nlm.nih.gov/public/Tuberculosis-Chest-X-ray-Datasets/Montgomery-County-CXR-Set/MontgomerySet/index.html. Shenzhen TB datasets released by the U.S. National Library of Medicine (SZ): URL: https://data.lhncbc.nlm.nih.gov/public/Tuberculosis-Chest-X-ray-Datasets/Shenzhen-Hospital-CXR-Set/index.html.

## Ethical Compliance and Usage Notes
- All images are anonymized and contain no personally identifiable information.
- The datasets are intended strictly for **non-commercial research use**.
- Users must cite the original data sources and this repository when using the datasets.
